39:56.026 --> 39:58.227
Just one of you.

39:58.245 --> 39:59.829
Step out

39:59.864 --> 40:02.782
If you think you got
the fucking balls.

40:08.405 --> 40:10.173
Get them dago
sons of bitches!

40:10.207 --> 40:13.042
( men shouting )

40:21.936 --> 40:23.686
( shouts )

40:31.729 --> 40:34.063
( screaming )

40:54.552 --> 40:56.252
Take that back to chicago.

40:57.421 --> 41:00.056
( groans )

41:05.262 --> 41:07.263
Worker:
<i>He's got a gun!</i>

41:07.297 --> 41:10.567
<i>( shouting fades )</i>

41:43.000 --> 41:44.884
<i>( gunshot )</i>

41:44.935 --> 41:47.003
( gunshot )

41:52.193 --> 41:54.510
Frank!

42:07.858 --> 42:09.993
( gunfire stops )

42:16.366 --> 42:17.967
Frank!

42:22.756 --> 42:24.891
<i>( door opens )</i>

42:40.774 --> 42:44.393
I called you 10 times.

42:44.411 --> 42:46.529
I'm here.

42:47.865 --> 42:49.999
<i>Did I do something wrong?</i>

42:51.001 --> 42:52.869
Not to me.

42:58.592 --> 43:00.927
You were very cold
when I found you.

43:03.080 --> 43:05.915
I must have
just fallen asleep.

43:07.635 --> 43:09.886
How you feeling now?

43:09.920 --> 43:12.021
Better.

43:14.141 --> 43:15.775
Rough day?

43:16.927 --> 43:18.811
Or shouldn't I ask?

43:24.068 --> 43:26.202
What were you doing
in the powder room?

43:28.438 --> 43:30.907
Cleaning this up
for you.

43:30.941 --> 43:32.825
Found it lying
on the floor.

43:36.964 --> 43:38.614
That's--
that's just--

43:38.666 --> 43:40.950
Yeah, I know what it is.

43:42.886 --> 43:44.804
Does that help you?

43:46.456 --> 43:48.675
Not anymore.

43:48.726 --> 43:51.293
How does that
make you feel?

43:56.400 --> 43:58.467
Terrified.

44:04.325 --> 44:06.475
I must repulse you.

44:06.493 --> 44:09.812
No. I know
about weakness.

44:10.864 --> 44:13.166
And I know about sin.

44:14.651 --> 44:17.370
You don't know
about me.

44:22.926 --> 44:24.711
Then tell me

44:24.762 --> 44:27.680
If that would make
any of this better.

44:32.886 --> 44:35.221
Roy...

44:41.812 --> 44:44.480
I have done
the most awful things.

45:04.218 --> 45:05.701
<i>Tuch.</i>

45:05.719 --> 45:08.204
<i>Manufaktur.</i>

45:08.222 --> 45:11.340
<i>Und konfektionsgeschaft.</i>

45:11.374 --> 45:12.425
<i>Karstadt.</i>

45:12.476 --> 45:14.093
Selby:
<i>That's a mouthful.</i>

45:14.144 --> 45:16.045
We just say
department store.

45:16.063 --> 45:17.346
What is that?

45:17.380 --> 45:19.065
This is something
we've been waiting for.

45:19.099 --> 45:22.402
- Now it's arrived.
- From far across the seas.

45:22.436 --> 45:26.272
<i>Stellvertretender</i>
<i>direktor.</i>

45:26.323 --> 45:28.057
Selby:
<i>Assistant manager.</i>

45:28.075 --> 45:29.742
Was that a good job?

45:29.777 --> 45:32.061
It was a position
of respect.

45:32.079 --> 45:34.664
- Watch over the employees.
- Make sure nobody steals.

45:34.698 --> 45:37.066
There were many
responsibilities.

45:37.084 --> 45:39.368
And they all
depended on loyalty,
didn't they?

45:39.402 --> 45:41.587
Loyalty and honesty.

45:41.622 --> 45:44.340
- You pride yourself on that.
- I strive.

45:44.374 --> 45:47.627
You strive.
You strive.

45:47.678 --> 45:49.595
Did you even
tell your wife?

45:49.630 --> 45:52.098
- <i>Your sons?</i>
- Knox: <i>Or just leave</i>
<i>with the money?</i>

45:52.132 --> 45:54.300
Selby:
<i>The money and mistress.</i>

45:54.351 --> 45:56.719
Knox:
<i>She worked behind</i>
<i>the lingerie counter.</i>

45:56.753 --> 45:58.638
How long did that last?

45:59.690 --> 46:01.774
Not long.

46:01.809 --> 46:04.093
So much for happiness,
huh, ed?

46:06.613 --> 46:10.233
I am a legal resident
of the United States.

46:10.267 --> 46:12.201
You are what
I say you are.

46:12.236 --> 46:14.320
And I say
you don't belong here.

46:14.371 --> 46:16.622
Then deport me.

46:16.657 --> 46:20.960
( speaking german )

46:24.281 --> 46:26.582
( speaks german )

46:26.616 --> 46:28.835
I was army intelligence
during the war.

46:28.886 --> 46:31.254
I thought the language
was very beautiful.

46:34.892 --> 46:38.728
"a father rides with his son
through night and wind.

46:38.762 --> 46:41.314
<i>The child is terrified.</i>

46:41.348 --> 46:43.516
<i>A demon in the woods.</i>

46:43.567 --> 46:45.351
<i>The elfking."</i>

46:46.737 --> 46:48.771
What does
the father say, ed?

46:48.805 --> 46:53.142
( speaking german )

46:53.160 --> 46:55.828
- "only a wisp of fog."
- <i>ja.</i>

46:55.863 --> 46:58.164
<i>But the father is wrong</i>
<i>and the elfking is real</i>

46:58.198 --> 47:02.084
And the son--
what happens to the son,
ed, in beautiful german?

47:02.119 --> 47:04.453
( speaking german )

47:10.177 --> 47:12.512
"in his arms

47:12.546 --> 47:14.714
The child was dead."

47:15.599 --> 47:17.266
<i>Ja.</i>

47:21.638 --> 47:24.941
Your boys,
konrad and lucas,
they're grown men now.

47:24.975 --> 47:26.893
Lucas has a son
of his own.

47:26.944 --> 47:29.645
- What?
- They changed
their last name.

47:29.679 --> 47:31.781
As if you
didn't even exist.

47:31.815 --> 47:34.683
To escape the shame
their father the thief,

47:34.701 --> 47:38.187
<i>The liar,</i>
<i>the traitor</i>

47:38.205 --> 47:40.406
<i>Brought upon them.</i>

47:40.457 --> 47:43.826
Six days from now,
you'll be in the custody
of the hanover police.

47:43.860 --> 47:47.463
<i>Then you and your boys</i>
<i>can get acquainted</i>
<i>all over again.</i>

47:47.530 --> 47:50.249
Think how glad
they'll be to see you.

47:55.138 --> 47:57.706
What do you want
from me?

47:57.724 --> 47:59.642
We want you
to tell us something.

47:59.676 --> 48:02.645
What? What?

48:02.679 --> 48:04.764
I do not know.

48:06.316 --> 48:08.317
What do you
want me to say?

48:08.352 --> 48:11.153
- You decide.
- You decide and you can go.

48:13.106 --> 48:15.557
I do not understand.

48:19.329 --> 48:21.197
It's very simple, ed.

48:21.231 --> 48:23.950
You tell us one thing,
one little thing,

48:24.001 --> 48:26.369
And we're done for today.
You have my word.

48:26.403 --> 48:29.088
Call it a demonstration
of loyalty.

48:37.431 --> 48:39.632
( paper rustles )

48:45.472 --> 48:48.107
Ralph capone.

48:48.976 --> 48:50.526
Yes?

48:50.560 --> 48:53.262
At the train station.

48:54.481 --> 48:57.867
That was the man
