48:59.436 --> 49:01.203
Why?

49:09.663 --> 49:12.281
( sobbing )
because...

49:12.299 --> 49:16.669
That is what Nucky
told me to do.

49:27.264 --> 49:29.231
See how easy that was?

49:48.368 --> 49:50.652
Ed...

49:52.089 --> 49:54.206
We'll see you
again soon.

50:33.797 --> 50:35.864
I get off a train...

50:37.834 --> 50:40.386
And right there

50:40.420 --> 50:42.371
In a newspaper...

50:53.049 --> 50:56.068
What was wrong
with brooklyn, huh?

50:56.103 --> 50:58.738
We was all happy there.

50:58.772 --> 51:02.274
Al says,
"come out," and...

51:11.418 --> 51:14.286
He wants to speak
to you personal.

51:20.743 --> 51:22.845
Go on.

51:48.705 --> 51:51.290
There's not much
more to go on.

51:52.409 --> 51:55.161
Word is they were
chicago detectives.

51:55.212 --> 51:57.663
A special squad.

51:57.714 --> 51:59.965
They say someone called
and told them

52:00.000 --> 52:04.470
