couldn't be trusted.

52:07.290 --> 52:09.625
He never got
his gun out.

52:13.796 --> 52:15.397
( sniffles )

52:17.634 --> 52:21.970
Every fucking thing
that crawls

52:21.988 --> 52:23.906
Is gonna pay.

52:25.692 --> 52:27.827
<i>( al crying )</i>

52:46.496 --> 52:48.964
( kisses )

52:52.102 --> 52:54.937
( sobbing )

53:26.503 --> 53:29.138
Clayton davies?

53:29.172 --> 53:31.724
We're with
the philadelphia police.

53:34.060 --> 53:37.045
<i>( ukulele playing )</i>

53:52.779 --> 53:54.947
<i>( knocking )</i>

53:58.067 --> 54:00.235
<i>( knocking )</i>

54:07.677 --> 54:09.845
You're not supposed
to be up here.

54:09.879 --> 54:12.748
Then you better not
let anyone see me.

54:20.440 --> 54:23.192
Do you know
what happened?

54:24.594 --> 54:26.695
They arrested clayton.

54:26.730 --> 54:29.114
What do you mean?

54:29.149 --> 54:31.933
The police came
and they arrested him.

54:31.952 --> 54:34.320
They said
he poisoned henry.

54:38.241 --> 54:41.076
Why would somebody
do something like that?

54:51.254 --> 54:53.789
( crying )

55:03.466 --> 55:05.651
<i>( seagulls screeching )</i>

55:05.685 --> 55:08.821
<i>( boat horn blaring )</i>

55:46.359 --> 55:48.694
<i>The hell</i>
<i>happened to you?</i>

55:51.781 --> 55:53.699
What do you mean?

55:58.521 --> 56:00.372
You look like
you slept on a bench.

56:00.407 --> 56:03.208
I spent the night
with old friends.

56:03.243 --> 56:06.078
There was much drinking.
Too much.

56:06.129 --> 56:08.497
And the night
became morning.

56:08.531 --> 56:10.549
If you're going to disappear
for an entire day--

56:10.583 --> 56:12.200
It will not happen again.

56:12.218 --> 56:15.370
I shouldn't have
to worry about that.
You understand?

56:17.807 --> 56:19.425
That's all I'm saying.

56:19.476 --> 56:23.011
It's a responsibility
that you asked for.

56:29.569 --> 56:32.905
- Have you eaten?
- I am not hungry.

56:34.390 --> 56:36.075
Suit yourself.

56:41.414 --> 56:43.064
<i>Hold on.</i>

56:46.252 --> 56:48.236
Come over here.

57:09.025 --> 57:10.976
Well?

